<F P=103> BK1901155794 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA Jan 19 -- Nong Duc Manh, politburo member 
of the C.C. [Central Committee] of Vietnam Communist Party and 
chairman of the National Assembly received here today Prof. Dr. 
I. Kalantari, minister of agriculture of Iran who is on a visit 
to Vietnam. 
  Chairman Nong Duc Manh and Minister I. Kalantari exchanged 
views on organization and activities of the two national 
assemblies of Vietnam and Iran. 
  Minister Kalantari informed Chairman Manh of the results of 
his visit to Vietnam and conveyed the Iranian Parliament 
president's invitation to the latter to visit Iran. 
