<H3> <TI>   Hata Comments on Threatened U.S. Sanctions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1601140694 Tokyo NIHON KEIZAI SHIMBUN in Japanese 14 Jan 
94 Evening Edition p 2--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1601140694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo NIHON KEIZAI SHIMBUN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Japanese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At a news conference on 14 January after a cabinet 
meeting, Tsutomu Hata, deputy prime minister and foreign 
minister, commented on a 20 January time limit for U.S. 
