  [Text] The commander of the Royal Brunei Navy [RBN] is in 
Singapore on a goodwill visit. It is Colonel Kafi Razali's 
first official visit to Singapore since taking over as commander 
of RBN last June. This morning he called on Defense Minister Dr 
Yeo Ning Hong. He also met with the chief of Navy, Commodore 
