  [Text] Pyongyang, January 19 (KCNA) -- Production is on the 
constant increase in different sectors of the national economy 
in the Democratic People's Republic of Korea. 
  The Songsan mine overfulfilled its January plan on all 
indices on January 14. 
  Entering the new year, the Musan mining complex is topping 
its daily assignments by 30 percent in the production of iron 
headings. 
