Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Commenting on the 21 January remarks by a North 
Korean Foreign Ministry spokesman carried by the North Korean 
Central News Agency, ROK Nuclear Ambassador Kim Sam-hun has said 
that "it is not time to express our clear-cut position on North 
Korea's attitude." He also said: "The statement by a Foreign 
Ministry spokesman was intended, in part, to make the 
negotiations between North Korea and the International Atomic 
Energy Agency [IAEA] difficult and, in another part, to pacify 
